Be careful, this map is HARD !!
==================

Hello guys ! (sorry for my bad english)

That map is an obstacle-race map!! You start on a raft and have to jump over the obstacles, avoid the rockets, and be careful!!! If you come first at the end, you will have the choice between T SPawn, CT Spawn, and go to the TOP !!! 

Enjoy guys!!!!!!!!! =)
